<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your Finder Reward Is Ready — Citizen Link</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f6f9; font-family:'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width:600px;">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="background-color:#003b5a; border-radius:12px 12px 0 0; padding:28px 40px;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; letter-spacing:-0.3px;">Citizen Link</p>
              <p style="margin:6px 0 0; font-size:12px; color:#a8cfe0; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-transform:uppercase;">Trusted Civic Services</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#1d9e75; padding:12px 40px;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; text-align:center; letter-spacing:0.3px;">
                YOUR FINDER REWARD IS READY TO WITHDRAW
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#ffffff; padding:40px; border-left:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-right:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 12px; font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#003b5a; line-height:1.3;">
                Great news — your reward is waiting!
              </h1>
              <p style="margin:0 0 24px; font-size:15px; color:#475569; line-height:1.7;">
                Thank you for reuniting someone with their lost document. The owner has completed payment and your finder reward of
                <strong style="color:#1d9e75;">KES {{amount}}</strong> has been credited to your Citizen Link wallet.
              </p>

              <!-- Reward summary card -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
                style="background-color:#f0fdf4; border:1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:28px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:20px 24px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 12px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#1d9e75; letter-spacing:0.8px; text-transform:uppercase;">Reward Details</p>
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:13px; color:#64748b; width:45%;">Disbursement Reference</td>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#0f172a;">#{{disbursementNumber}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:13px; color:#64748b;">Reward Amount</td>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#1d9e75;">KES {{amount}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:13px; color:#64748b;">Status</td>
                        <td style="padding:5px 0; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#0f172a;">
                          <span style="background-color:#dcfce7; color:#166534; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:4px; font-size:12px;">Available</span>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px; font-size:14px; color:#475569; line-height:1.7;">
                To receive your reward, open the Citizen Link app, navigate to your <strong>Wallet</strong>, and tap <strong>Withdraw</strong> next to this disbursement.
                The funds will be sent directly to your M-Pesa account.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:0 0 8px; font-size:14px; color:#475569; line-height:1.7;">
                Make sure your M-Pesa phone number is up to date in your profile settings before withdrawing.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-top:none; border-radius:0 0 12px 12px; padding:24px 40px; text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 4px; font-size:12px; color:#94a3b8;">Citizen Link &mdash; Trusted Civic Services</p>
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:11px; color:#cbd5e1;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
